name: Eshish Multipack
description:
The Eshish is the worlds first luxury portable electronic shisha device. It is designed to provide the finest and ultimate smoking experience without any of the harmful toxins. It offers the freshest taste yet to be available on the market. Along with the bold colours, the crystal glowing tip sets you apart from the crowd introducing you to a whole new world of smoking in a healthier way.

This Multipack contains five different fruity flavours; Grape, Blueberry, Strawberry, Peach, and Apple.

TECHNICAL DATA:

- Up to 300 puffs per stick
- Single unit 120mm x 12mm 
- RoHS Approved
- CE Approved
- Legal to use indoors in the UK
- No known Health Risks

<strong>UK First Class Delivery<strong> 
<strong>Items will be delivered within 1 working day<strong>

*Not intended for persons under the age of 18
